"{\"uid\": \"kbzk.com-news-local-news-manhattan-marksman-going-for-gold-in-shooting-at-the-2024-paris-olympics\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"MANHATTAN - At just seven years old, Ivan Roe's father signed him up for a gun safety and hunter's education class.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 115, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ivan Roe's father\", \"from\": 37, \"to\": 54}, {\"ngram\": \"a gun safety\", \"from\": 73, \"to\": 85}, {\"ngram\": \"hunter's education class\", \"from\": 90, \"to\": 114}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fast forward to today, and he's getting ready to compete in the 2024 Olympic Games in competitive shooting.\", \"from\": 116, \"to\": 223, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"today\", \"from\": 132, \"to\": 137}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 176, \"to\": 198}, {\"ngram\": \"competitive shooting\", \"from\": 202, \"to\": 222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Coming all the way from Manhattan, Ivan says it's the opportunity of a lifetime.\", \"from\": 224, \"to\": 304, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 248, \"end\": 257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.982167047776057, \"rank\": 0.018156738103945746, \"text\": \"Manhattan\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ivan\", \"from\": 259, \"to\": 263}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 289}, {\"ngram\": \"a lifetime\", \"from\": 293, \"to\": 303}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's pretty much a pinnacle achievement of your life, something you might not ever be able to do again,\\\" said Roe.\", \"from\": 306, \"to\": 421, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a pinnacle achievement\", \"from\": 324, \"to\": 346}, {\"ngram\": \"your life\", \"from\": 350, \"to\": 359}, {\"ngram\": \"Roe\", \"from\": 417, \"to\": 420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Growing up in the small-town atmosphere of Manhattan with less than 50 people in his graduating class, Ivan Roe has big dreams.\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 550, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 466, \"end\": 475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.982167047776057, \"rank\": 0.018156738103945746, \"text\": \"Manhattan\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the small-town atmosphere\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 462}, {\"ngram\": \"less than 50 people\", \"from\": 481, \"to\": 500}, {\"ngram\": \"his graduating class\", \"from\": 504, \"to\": 524}, {\"ngram\": \"Ivan Roe\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 534}, {\"ngram\": \"big dreams\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 549}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There were definitely times where I thought, \\\"well, what if I make it-it would be cool to be the first Olympian from Manhattan,\\\" said Roe.\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 691, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 656, \"end\": 664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999933353525821, \"rank\": 6.6511630533390635e-06, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 670, \"end\": 679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.982167047776057, \"rank\": 0.018156738103945746, \"text\": \"Manhattan\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 580}, {\"ngram\": \"Roe\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 690}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For several years, Roe set out on a mission to earn his spot on Team USA in competitive shooting.\", \"from\": 693, \"to\": 790, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 757, \"end\": 765, \"title\": 